metadata.name: Caten8ted Logo #0  #1/222
metadata.description: First design for Caten8ted. The ownership of this nft will enable an experiment with design composability with Digital and IRL goods. The design will be redeemable for an upcoming merch drop that utilizes the work purchased. The design will be burned upon redemption, or can be held for the next iteration of this project. This is the genesis block of an web3 enabled design experiment by Caten8ted.
